<blockquote>
*The submitted avatar should be around 167cm (~5'6") to 180cm (~6'0").
* The avatar '''must''' have both a PC and Android version.
* The PC and Android versions '''must''' fit within the restrictions set forth by the '''Good''' Avatar Performance Rank for their respective platforms (links: PC, Android).
* The PC version '''should''' use higher-fidelity textures, meshes, and shaders where applicable.
* The avatar '''must''' have some form of visemes. Ideally, you should use blend-shape visemes, but jaw flap is acceptable.
* The avatar '''must''' match aesthetically between PC and Android.
* You may use Gesture Overrides on both Android and PC versions, but they can only modify the face blendshapes for emoting.
* You may include emotes on both Android and PC versions, but they can only animate blendshapes or bone rotation/translations.
* Neither PC nor Android can use "gesture props", "inventory systems", or other complex gesture or emote-activated systems.
* The avatar thumbnail should include your VRChat username (if you want), and must also not violate the VRChat [[Special:MyLanguage/Terms of Service|Terms of Service]] or [[Special:MyLanguage/Community Guidelines|Community Guideline]].</blockquote>